title: Welcome home to VIP treatment!
posting_body: ['Text 9840B for more info!', 'Are you ready to make your move into a new home?', ' I’d like to help!', ' As a native to Dallas, with 10 years of experience in the rental housing market, I know how to help you in the most efficient and productive way.', ' I have access to thousands of apartments, condos and houses, including the private market.', 'I will not send you random properties, that may or may not be a good fit and that may or may not have anything available.', ' I will send you direct links to the actual property, with up-to-date availability, pricing and floor plans.', ' Once you decide on the properties that are a good fit for you, I will map out a plan and schedule tours, on your behalf, for each individual property.', 'Let me do the work and all you have to do is point and click and show up for the appointment.', 'How do I get paid for my services, you may ask?', ' I get paid by the management company that you choose to lease from.', ' My services are free to you!', ' All that is needed is that you write my name down, on the application, as the referring agent that help you.', 'Disclaimer:  I do not service short term housing.', ' You will have to call the property directly to ask for corporate housing or short-term rental options.', 'Must have excellent rental history, no criminal background record and valid bank records or an offer letter to validate income of three times the rent.', ' Credit scores don’t need to be perfect, as long as you don’t owe any properties money.', 'I look forward to helping you make your home search an easy success!', 'Everything you need at your doorstep', 'When you live at Amelia at Farmers Market, local shopping, dining, and nightlife are all right at your doorstep.', 'The Dallas Farmers Market gives you convenient access to local groceries and artisans.', 'The Main Street District and Deep Ellum are both within a 10-minute walk, putting countless entertainment options as walkable amenities.', 'Come home to VIP treatment, as you enjoy the city’s best rooftop pool, fifth-floor Sky Lounge overlooking the city, Ladies Wine Bar, the Man Cave, and the Community Library.', 'At Amelia, we’ve considered every detail, including conveniences like Nest thermostats, a Bark Park, car charging stations, and electronic refrigerated package lockers.', 'Throughout your new home, you’ll enjoy countless thoughtful touches that will pamper you and impress your guests.']
